title: Grateful Dead Live at Charlotte Coliseum on 1995-03-24
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Stagger Lee, Minglewood Blues, High Time, If The Shoe Fits, Black Throated Wind*, Bird Song, Promised Land (65 Mins.)

Set 2

Here Comes Sunshine, Samba In The Rain, Women Are Smarter, Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> The Last Time-> Black Peter-> Around & Around, E: Liberty (88 Mins.)

* Weir on acoustic
